  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(145, 145, 145);white-space:normal;font-weight:normal;font-size:14px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 14px;margin:13px 0px 0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">整理｜华卫</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">3 月 1 日，智谱交出了 2025 年度业绩报告，这是其上市近三个月后的首份年度财报。今年 1 月 8 日，智谱登陆港交所，股价从发行价 116.2 港元一度冲至近 700 港元，目前市值超 3000 亿港元。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">这份业绩报告喜忧参半，其收入激增但亦被分析师评增长低于预期，且综合毛利率不佳。智谱表示，公司预计通过收入增长和提升运营效率实现盈利，但尚未给出具体时间表。智谱还在财报中传达了一个信号，将继续加大投资，增加国产芯片在训练模型中的使用。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;color: #00b38b;text-align: left;line-height: 35px;margin: 40px 8px 0 8px;background: none no-repeat left 28px;background-size: 100% 6px;background-image: url(&quot;https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=be88777f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FhLLZnAbUwNiahssb8Fokm6wmYOAXQI8Ha8mCev3ZeWudibCZvgN2fQge0Cxpod3hbEbrJ0sWA71KzFhBGEIus4OvrNiabVlXmpVRcQqZYDmczA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg&quot;);\"><span style=\"display: block;font-size: 32px;margin-bottom: 10px;padding-left: 22px;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;网友吵疯了：完美政策还是推广义务? </span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">财报显示，智谱 2025 年营收 7.24 亿元，同比增长 131.9%；毛利 2.97 亿元，同比增长 68.7%；毛利率为 41.0%，较上年的 56.3% 下降 15.3 个百分点；年内亏损 47.18 亿元，同比扩大 59.5%；经调整后净亏损 31.82 亿元，同比扩大 29.1%；研发投入 31.8 亿元，同比增长 44.9%。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4666666666666667\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;vertical-align: baseline;height: auto !important;width: 661px !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100176533\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d95528d3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm6icckJ6dqHJYkB2tO9P7szv0O8zOv9XoZPsKNdT4U1iakhe6VhQb2T1E5TuibGJ2Fgz92iaSQrc3LHMqUfwreNMeNkYE4vficXvORU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D1\"></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">从营收情况来看，智谱是一家典型的大模型公司：收入增长很快，但亏损巨大；研发投入仍然非常重，强度达营收的 4.4 倍。此外，智谱的毛利率下降明显，整体综合毛利率由 2024 年的 56.3% 降至 41.0%。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">收入结构上，智谱 2025 年以本地化部署服务为主。其中，本地化部署服务收入 5.34 亿元，同比增长 102.3%，占总收入的 73.7%；云端部署服务收入 1.90 亿元，同比增长 292.6%，占比 26.3%。需要注意的是，2025 年智谱这两种服务模式的毛利率变化不一。云端部署毛利率从上年的 3.3% 提升到 18.9%，改善不小；但本地化部署毛利率则从 66.0% 下降到 48.8%。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4111111111111111\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;vertical-align: baseline;height: auto !important;width: 661px !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100176534\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d455ff94&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm60lP6NIeriaMTicG5cElr842pAGDIETOCoGOflGPpouiaxkkiaOoKwefBrfoft3exGnGDQDMVMrT2UP1BuL6BQw0lZYAAdfoobRE4%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D2\"></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">财报中对此的解释是，云端部署业务主要由于模型推理效率提升、算力规模扩张导致边际成本递减，同时价格有所增加；即通过对推理侧的极致工程优化，在大幅度降低单位成本的同时，实现了毛利表现的稳健提升；本地化部署业务由于为满足客户需求而投入了更多的交付资源。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">具体按业务形态与核心产品线来拆分，智谱 2025 年的企业级通用大模型收入 3.66 亿元，占比 50.4%；开放平台及 API 收入 1.90 亿元，占比 26.3%；企业级智能体收入 1.66 亿元，占比 22.9%；技术服务及其他收入占比低。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 